{"tid":9834,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"每一位啱啱分左手既你","createTime":"2016-11-28T17:12:06.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T15:58:26.000Z","uid":22790,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"51b67a9b7f2e74c20b6f78a3a1c88b5878b98140","tid":9834,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:12:07.000Z","msg":"我都係啱啱分手冇耐<br />\n一齊左都算長時間 一開始係好傷心好痛 覺得成個世界好黑暗<br />\n好似個天冧左 一個好愛好愛既人離開我<br />\n個人好冇動力 冇胃口 失眠 甚至發夢都會嚇醒<br />\n<br />\n但我想講既係 要離開既人你唔會留得住 我試過求過 跪過 一眼都冇望過我<br />\n係最後一刻留返少少尊嚴比自己<br />\n唔好再搵佢 唔好煩佢<br />\n唔好晒時間係佢背後等佢<br />\n反而要將自己變得更好<br />\n要超越佢 要行係佢前面 比佢見到你<br />\n就算佢冇因爲你變好左有所動搖<br />\n但你已經改變左 前面會有更好既等待你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然我都係講比自己聽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b4dda5bf99c5c2b338d8848656e4dbf3f4a963","tid":9834,"uid":1524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:38:46.000Z","msg":"隨緣啦施主。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0463a9fa3ce054f365b15c50a3520f1c6fd98c","tid":9834,"uid":21007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:39:04.000Z","msg":"時間沖淡一切，最緊要家下睇得開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1855f3df02d4e913927d6dc6d9eab688497ef77","tid":9834,"uid":1943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:41:04.000Z","msg":"講就容易 做就好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b1428ef929555c5d09384caa484568418c86dd","tid":9834,"uid":16395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:42:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講就容易 做就好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n能醫不自醫 不知同人講過幾多次<br />\n自己就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e566b0363f42355d8fe8a608d8abc4269a6621","tid":9834,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:12:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隨緣啦施主。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大家咁話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a00e7d4a31c9e0b6ce5443d9055ee036619da6a","tid":9834,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:12:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>時間沖淡一切，最緊要家下睇得開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係有時夜晚會諗起 但同人傾下呻下 原來又一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8302a3ef570051c1a91cad937d52c886125938a5","tid":9834,"uid":20329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:13:29.000Z","msg":"一齊努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa72955ab3453be842a19810895c9834e78bac89","tid":9834,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:19:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講就容易 做就好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n能醫不自醫 不知同人講過幾多次<br />\n自己就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當然我都有經歷過一哭二鬧三上吊既情節<br />\n但當我做齊所有野佢都唔返轉頭甚至開始憎我<br />\n咁我就明佢已經唔愛我 一個愛你既人唔會捨得你傷心 唔會捨得淨返你一個面對<br />\n愛情裡 不愛面前 所以野都係不值一提<br />\n既然佢都唔愛我 我更加唔可以連自己都唔愛自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be02756ffe0ddbd4fe45019daef7e33b323143d3","tid":9834,"uid":15339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:20:34.000Z","msg":"都係分左無耐<br />\n傷心就實有<br />\n不過對比初戀俾人飛<br />\n今次真係好快收拾到心情<br />\n<br />\n加油絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216924c94b9aead2913d344a0921d786b0b7cc51","tid":9834,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:20:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一齊努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都要加油啊 我已經捱過左一星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b07980b1e0ce1afbdc7e53ab41f47432ba8b3a1","tid":9834,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:20:50.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"b14cb76ad379395d49033de741739277774498be","tid":9834,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:26:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都係分左無耐<br />\n傷心就實有<br />\n不過對比初戀俾人飛<br />\n今次真係好快收拾到心情<br />\n<br />\n加油絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我一開始真係好傷心 一齊四年半 <br />\n因為佢變心分手 一日之後佢已經同左人一齊 我有諗過做傻事 但最後好多好朋友鬧醒我<br />\n所以大家要一齊努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b18719abf95d87680a0eeda55020edbec8589733","tid":9834,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:27:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好收埋自己啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d32889ed3bfaefeb6d27bcc0aa042797e6bdab","tid":9834,"uid":2433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:32:04.000Z","msg":"找對的人- 張敬軒"},{"pid":"f410bf2c267f503d62bd77a775745885244f8e78","tid":9834,"uid":15339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:41:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>都係分左無耐<br />\n傷心就實有<br />\n不過對比初戀俾人飛<br />\n今次真係好快收拾到心情<br />\n<br />\n加油絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我一開始真係好傷心 一齊四年半 <br />\n因為佢變心分手 一日之後佢已經同左人一齊 我有諗過做傻事 但最後好多好朋友鬧醒我<br />\n所以大家要一齊努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁快同第二個又真係好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩你無做傻事!!<br />\n呢啲人唔值得你咁做<br />\n希望你早日搵到個識珍惜你既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ac10341ab0fbd489d505bcc570c64d03110368","tid":9834,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:43:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>找對的人- 張敬軒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 夠正面 順手唱埋藍天一定喊唔出"},{"pid":"0199670711ba258e301f27a191bb0b02639f18c8","tid":9834,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:49:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>都係分左無耐<br />\n傷心就實有<br />\n不過對比初戀俾人飛<br />\n今次真係好快收拾到心情<br />\n<br />\n加油絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我一開始真係好傷心 一齊四年半 <br />\n因為佢變心分手 一日之後佢已經同左人一齊 我有諗過做傻事 但最後好多好朋友鬧醒我<br />\n所以大家要一齊努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁快同第二個又真係好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩你無做傻事!!<br />\n呢啲人唔值得你咁做<br />\n希望你早日搵到個識珍惜你既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個個仲要係佢話佢當兄弟既女仔朋友黎<br />\n其實佢一早就安排好要分手 跟本我就同戴帽冇分別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我信有報應"},{"pid":"c00fc024dfe2c6ad7859c574f339af4f04890f1b","tid":9834,"uid":8228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:56:29.000Z","msg":"大家努力<br />\n啱啱分開一定難過<br />\n一日24個鐘都好似變咗48個鐘咁<br />\n慢慢嚟 時間會沖淡一切<br />\n呢一刻唔好做傻事就得<br />\n總會有人更值得你去珍惜"},{"pid":"aa41356b2eef4dafba737d26e2978d3f9250a487","tid":9834,"uid":29148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T19:00:51.000Z","msg":"樓主好正面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bdccf7da5f634cd64cfa12313e6b360313bfa9c","tid":9834,"uid":37185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T19:02:07.000Z","msg":"我都想試下分手"},{"pid":"23a32b22f397282e7cafd210b6cda409d011ddaa","tid":9834,"uid":23107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T19:04:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>都係分左無耐<br />\n傷心就實有<br />\n不過對比初戀俾人飛<br />\n今次真係好快收拾到心情<br />\n<br />\n加油絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我一開始真係好傷心 一齊四年半 <br />\n因為佢變心分手 一日之後佢已經同左人一齊 我有諗過做傻事 但最後好多好朋友鬧醒我<br />\n所以大家要一齊努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都試過，上左佢屋企發曬顛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77390b734a6974857e9a263b274198cfd57736b5","tid":9834,"uid":14304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T19:08:40.000Z","msg":"都係可以做嘅都做過曬<br />\n一個人對你冇feel 真係做咩都冇用<br />\n過左兩個禮拜之後佢已經同第二個一齊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5511821e299b42cea429b0b0c80c58c7ce6b7df","tid":9834,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T19:10:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家努力<br />\n啱啱分開一定難過<br />\n一日24個鐘都好似變咗48個鐘咁<br />\n慢慢嚟 時間會沖淡一切<br />\n呢一刻唔好做傻事就得<br />\n總會有人更值得你去珍惜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n時間真係會沖淡一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d89e77850f019fbdb2e827fed1e72367b6f97f76","tid":9834,"uid":15872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T19:13:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ec929de7264fac6187896e52627fab83d366a1","tid":9834,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T19:14:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主好正面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有一陣子好負面嫁 但可能係因為綠帽影響同朋友屋企人支持我 <br />\n所以希望有人如果分手唔開心<br />\n睇到之後會明白你只不過失去左一個唔愛你既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930e85676a1a2401832bb8140a4fa1fb1c36afbf","tid":9834,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T19:15:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想試下分手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哩個我有啲難開解你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f21b22147344a3e8d402e7ed83e98185389dd30a","tid":9834,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T19:17:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>都係分左無耐<br />\n傷心就實有<br />\n不過對比初戀俾人飛<br />\n今次真係好快收拾到心情<br />\n<br />\n加油絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我一開始真係好傷心 一齊四年半 <br />\n因為佢變心分手 一日之後佢已經同左人一齊 我有諗過做傻事 但最後好多好朋友鬧醒我<br />\n所以大家要一齊努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都試過，上左佢屋企發曬顛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我本身約左佢30號見 想對佢發癲比佢睇我有幾慘 <br />\n但有咩用 佢只會覺得自己最後揀其他人係啱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b4da4a7a4219ffd42b641a642ba68e765343f06","tid":9834,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T19:18:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩心事啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e611b77715da86030f896c7d2ee18f2e32dc7cb","tid":9834,"uid":16395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T19:19:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都係可以做嘅都做過曬<br />\n一個人對你冇feel 真係做咩都冇用<br />\n過左兩個禮拜之後佢已經同第二個一齊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsame here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要完始終都係會完"},{"pid":"8813e02e690810a1f6958b2ffba8e7beeae3826d","tid":9834,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T19:19:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都係可以做嘅都做過曬<br />\n一個人對你冇feel 真係做咩都冇用<br />\n過左兩個禮拜之後佢已經同第二個一齊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n放心 我一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我一日都可以咁正面 你都得 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ef864b1bc8cf40cfa6e33abcb3c37a8167cac9","tid":9834,"uid":2510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T19:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00e932c064595cd8596396e63b3572b9ff6918f7","tid":9834,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T19:20:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>都係可以做嘅都做過曬<br />\n一個人對你冇feel 真係做咩都冇用<br />\n過左兩個禮拜之後佢已經同第二個一齊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsame here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要完始終都係會完</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好衰比佢睇 咁傷心唔值得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f91a45edad76d5f5835bac6466f851d80683eb6","tid":9834,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T19:21:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇野面對唔到啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a8662efec3035a25e1dc3484a7db98d4ccadd3","tid":9834,"uid":12510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T19:22:47.000Z","msg":"時間會沖淡一切<br />\n<br />\n最緊要唔好因為唔開心而是旦搵個開始戀情<br />\n<br />\n利申：A1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"