實後生既你地大把機會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔少人都因為工作關係識唔到異性但自問條件唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 廿幾歲出頭半個老道</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都廿到半 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n廿幾歲人生仲有好長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f3999ee629ef474e4bd5a3d51bf7b094ca7ed5","tid":9834,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:12:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主好正面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有一陣子好負面嫁 但可能係因為綠帽影響同朋友屋企人支持我 <br />\n所以希望有人如果分手唔開心<br />\n睇到之後會明白你只不過失去左一個唔愛你既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我分左手一段時間 仲未放得低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家仲有keep住聯絡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好聯絡 信我 要忍手"},{"pid":"06f907599fb423c28b3a1070d35ef92855da9f15","tid":9834,"uid":20597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:13:01.000Z","msg":"最後我都係決定等。。"},{"pid":"43ab40b3c74ddbba6858516f12224e9199abf3ec","tid":9834,"uid":41844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:14:22.000Z","msg":"要走的人留不住<br />\n不走的人趕不走"},{"pid":"bbf16b2f41257dde6d8c19124dd362b6f9502311","tid":9834,"uid":20597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:15:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最後我都係決定等。。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一齊左四年 <br />\n佢同第二個一齊左 我仲要唔知 最後佢同我分手<br />\n之後抓爛塊臉係咁求佢都無用 <br />\n最後都係決定等。。<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c71a160246384f0d9bafbce2b3a80f221b436b2","tid":9834,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T18:32:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最後我都係決定等。。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一齊左四年 <br />\n佢同第二個一齊左 我仲要唔知 最後佢同我分手<br />\n之後抓爛塊臉係咁求佢都無用 <br />\n最後都係決定等。。<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係 四年半 原來出軌已經好耐 仲用所以野去美化自己出軌既事實<br />\n我冇話唔可以等 但你等既過程都可以增值自己 慢慢了解到生活冇左佢原來都可以生存到<br />\n到最後<br />\n等到既 恭喜你<br />\n等唔到既 一定會有下一個出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"847b5df723598416ef3ad0635868e9e0a6986d81","tid":9834,"uid":6085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:17:54.000Z","msg":"一齊加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24877d9e1f1471723bd3d679f82ca149dbb4226b","tid":9834,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:22:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你已經好叻"},{"pid":"e95cbc0ea20686db0bc35559881f1547c976d26d","tid":9834,"uid":23373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:27:30.000Z","msg":"希望下個更美好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9cc76e55dbdf9b27dd4d7c2cd99dbcafa429353","tid":9834,"uid":46504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:29:05.000Z","msg":"將自己變得更好（改變自己既過程好辛苦），佢可能會返嚟搵返你，然後到時唔理佢<br />\n<br />\n利申 過來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5c33cd8970dd140b054ab7a6615375a8db87d2e","tid":9834,"uid":8839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:29:34.000Z","msg":"幾日就放低左 我會唔會太仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8616c4479a3dd2c70b8427122f3306f2cc558e6f","tid":9834,"uid":41353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:31:48.000Z","msg":"我有時諗如果我地一心諗住要過得比佢更好令佢後悔，個出發點係咪其實都係佢"},{"pid":"d554d5b863fe1f37c731ec6081fbe41caec5ed9c","tid":9834,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:32:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  加油"},{"pid":"e14da55684e7ee7936f3e1a1375463812b5b6280","tid":9834,"uid":46504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:33:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我有時諗如果我地一心諗住要過得比佢更好令佢後悔，個出發點係咪其實都係佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係 但係得益既最終都係你"},{"pid":"0996be9b910b040c51d783e0ceb5274dbfc057c4","tid":9834,"uid":35481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T17:35:27.000Z","msg":"同樓主一樣，又喊又求過佢都無理過我。<br />\n佢淨係同我講:無人值得妳咁樣要失去尊嚴，放低自己去求佢咖，每個人都係平等咖。<br />\n一直去美化自己同佢分開既原因，<br />\n直到發現佢一早變左心有左第二個後，應該要醒啦，<br />\n但我依然仲未肯醒。<br />\n分開肯唔多一個月，佢有新女朋友，開心快活，<br />\n而我就繼續活係同佢既過去到。<br />\n我究竟幾時先肯放過自己。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b9fe0d0b609657e21abbc00185f51f11768266","tid":9834,"uid":12048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T17:38:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係啱啱分手冇耐<br />\n一齊左都算長時間 一開始係好傷心好痛 覺得成個世界好黑暗<br />\n好似個天冧左 一個好愛好愛既人離開我<br />\n個人好冇動力 冇胃口 失眠 甚至發夢都會嚇醒<br />\n<br />\n但我想講既係 要離開既人你唔會留得住 我試過求過 跪過 一眼都冇望過我<br />\n係最後一刻留返少少尊嚴比自己<br />\n唔好再搵佢 唔好煩佢<br />\n唔好晒時間係佢背後等佢<br />\n反而要將自己變得更好<br />\n要超越佢 要行係佢前面 比佢見到你<br />\n就算佢冇因爲你變好左有所動搖<br />\n但你已經改變左 前面會有更好既等待你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然我都係講比自己聽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我選擇左係佢背後等佢&hellip;"},{"pid":"2ffa77292ee936b09e873992276da6a7b878e72e","tid":9834,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T18:27:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一齊加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0db77bf371d83f23aa6305c1b767099e234bba","tid":9834,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T18:28:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你已經好叻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實唔叻 但我知我唔可以再令朋友擔心我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20a2317204ec2e3b773a8c7ae62408a0bcbe0b1f","tid":9834,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T18:28:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>希望下個更美好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都會嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"986f6b30995598b6c59b4e5e70aa6a9544f78083","tid":9834,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T18:29:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>將自己變得更好（改變自己既過程好辛苦），佢可能會返嚟搵返你，然後到時唔理佢<br />\n<br />\n利申 過來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我要後悔今日所做既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14f0b29426c3632ff0ef191bffa99337b17970db","tid":9834,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T18:30:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾日就放低左 我會唔會太仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每段關係結束都一定有一個人傷得重啲嫁喇 又唔可以話仆唔仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"821bc5dd3b976dd069db754a0e143559ad7de4a1","tid":9834,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T18:30:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  加油</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e445678211e37e95ee5b1525e9c825e845e09ec","tid":9834,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T18:32:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我有時諗如果我地一心諗住要過得比佢更好令佢後悔，個出發點係咪其實都係佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係 但係得益既最終都係你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n的確佢係令我前進既出發點 但既然放唔低咪當比個籍口自己去改變下自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19772715273997310be5fb867a9f412cd90fd55e","tid":9834,"uid":22790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T18:39:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同樓主一樣，又喊又求過佢都無理過我。<br />\n佢淨係同我講:無人值得妳咁樣要失去尊嚴，放低自己去求佢咖，每個人都係平等咖。<br />\n一直去美化自己同佢分開既原因，<br />\n直到發現佢一早變左心有左第二個後，應該要醒啦，<br />\n但我依然仲未肯醒。<br />\n分開肯唔多一個月，佢有新女朋友，開心快活，<br />\n而我就繼續活係同佢既過去到。<br />\n我究竟幾時先肯放過自己。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我今日又知道更多野 我知道佢背住我同人去街 呃我訓左原來去食宵夜 甚至拖住攬住其他人<br />\n其實我唔正面 我宜家做緊既就係不斷去聽多啲事實 去同自己講佢係賤人 狗男女 執到都喊三聲<br />\n我身邊既朋友每日都屌我 講啲好hurt既說話比我聽 真係好hurt好痛好難聽既說話 <br />\n但如果唔係佢地 我可能仲日日喊住咁要人安慰唔肯接受現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"165ebd17584d4b6ba7df9a11bc5a1c0cee2cf368","tid":9834,"uid":22790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T18:42:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都係啱啱分手冇耐<br />\n一齊左都算長時間 一開始係好傷心好痛 覺得成個世界好黑暗<br />\n好似個天冧左 一個好愛好愛既人離開我<br />\n個人好冇動力 冇胃口 失眠 甚至發夢都會嚇醒<br />\n<br />\n但我想講既係 要離開既人你唔會留得住 我試過求過 跪過 一眼都冇望過我<br />\n係最後一刻留返少少尊嚴比自己<br />\n唔好再搵佢 唔好煩佢<br />\n唔好晒時間係佢背後等佢<br />\n反而要將自己變得更好<br />\n要超越佢 要行係佢前面 比佢見到你<br />\n就算佢冇因爲你變好左有所動搖<br />\n但你已經改變左 前面會有更好既等待你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然我都係講比自己聽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我選擇左係佢背後等佢&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n與其係背後等佢不如行係佢前面<br />\n等佢後悔佢當日既決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de730f75e59f6481f8e0d3254a87e1c9c99537a","tid":9834,"uid":35481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T13:00:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同樓主一樣，又喊又求過佢都無理過我。<br />\n佢淨係同我講:無人值得妳咁樣要失去尊嚴，放低自己去求佢咖，每個人都係平等咖。<br />\n一直去美化自己同佢分開既原因，<br />\n直到發現佢一早變左心有左第二個後，應該要醒啦，<br />\n但我依然仲未肯醒。<br />\n分開肯唔多一個月，佢有新女朋友，開心快活，<br />\n而我就繼續活係同佢既過去到。<br />\n我究竟幾時先肯放過自己。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我今日又知道更多野 我知道佢背住我同人去街 呃我訓左原來去食宵夜 甚至拖住攬住其他人<br />\n其實我唔正面 我宜家做緊既就係不斷去聽多啲事實 去同自己講佢係賤人 狗男女 執到都喊三聲<br />\n我身邊既朋友每日都屌我 講啲好hurt既說話比我聽 真係好hurt好痛好難聽既說話 <br />\n但如果唔係佢地 我可能仲日日喊住咁要人安慰唔肯接受現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我憎佢唔落，呢樣先最慘。<br />\n事實就算證明佢有幾衰都好，自己就係嬲佢唔落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08b760e9d9ba47744c6fd91161abeee314d1a774","tid":9834,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T13:02:03.000Z","msg":"留名學做mk"},{"pid":"e7b5997ba054678e550ff84b8dc9e10745da6cc4","tid":9834,"uid":37912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T13:04:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}